{"tid":2114983,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"9寧波船員曾以免檢疫令留港及後確診 許樹昌稱有漏洞倡採樣本檢測","createTime":"2020-07-19T08:14:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-20T10:47:44.000Z","uid":123774,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b4c847b8c6521281887b91367e62484f50a0967d","tid":2114983,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:14:55.000Z","msg":"新型冠狀病毒肺炎疫情在全球持續蔓延，本港仍實施入境管制，但衞生署昨（6月30日）公布，有曾逗留香港的貨船船員抵內地後被驗出對新型肺炎呈陽性。由於貨船船員可獲豁免檢疫，早前入境香港時不需接受新冠病毒檢測。運輸及房屋局透露，由2月8日至6月21日，獲豁免的貨船船員類別人士約8000人。<br />\n<br />\n政府抗疫專家、香港中文大學呼吸系統科講座教授許樹昌指事件響起警號，現行做法明顯有漏洞，若有人來自高風險地區，抵港後在外出消費或到酒吧消遣，已可將病毒帶出去。他建議應為全部免檢疫者收集深喉唾液樣本做檢測，從高風險地區抵港人士則應於留港期間在酒店檢疫。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/492757/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9B%BE%E7%95%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E8%88%B9%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%A8%B1%E6%A8%B9%E6%98%8C%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%80%A1%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F492757%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E6%259B%25BE%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25B1%2581%25E5%2585%258D%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E7%2596%25AB%25E8%2588%25B9%25E5%2593%25A1%25E7%25A2%25BA%25E8%25A8%25BA-%25E8%25A8%25B1%25E6%25A8%25B9%25E6%2598%258C%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%259C%2589%25E6%25BC%258F%25E6%25B4%259E%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%258E%25A1%25E6%25A8%25A3%25E6%259C%25AC%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC&d=Se3jk6qONbDe%2BTgec%2FNeB2zUwbN2nhMFbUYjFdDHJd4%3D&h=ee28cfd3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/492757/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E6%9B%BE%E7%95%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%B1%81%E5%85%8D%E6%AA%A2%E7%96%AB%E8%88%B9%E5%93%A1%E7%A2%BA%E8%A8%BA-%E8%A8%B1%E6%A8%B9%E6%98%8C%E7%A8%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%BC%8F%E6%B4%9E%E5%80%A1%E6%8E%A1%E6%A8%A3%E6%9C%AC%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC</a>"},{"pid":"7c76aa5c4f217406f88b88d24786d24b1ed8c8e3","tid":2114983,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:18:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b62d59bd2c58004b9fd33c181c34339cf6cc33","tid":2114983,"uid":55162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:20:12.000Z","msg":"正苦繼續話唔關事"},{"pid":"12faec01bd024f9356bb296c1b4fb320ad4a6685","tid":2114983,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"29913343da0ad2c72c05a43eff9275a6c41f0ca4","tid":2114983,"uid":160373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:22:21.000Z","msg":"港共話唔關事<br />\n支共01報出嚟公然違反國安法"},{"pid":"b9cd778f5ba9fffa406b063d209769c5234b6448","tid":2114983,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:22:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d14f22c7a9608e50084612ccbf3f120bba0dc3","tid":2114983,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"林鄭4點記招完全冇講收緊免檢疫令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eeceeac18bb33377d9f8778cb9dfd9f9bd501605","tid":2114983,"uid":3860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0d14f22c7a9608e50084612ccbf3f120bba0dc3","tid":2114983,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"林鄭4點記招完全冇講收緊免檢疫令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:34:08.000Z","msg":"不嬲柒婆無論政治定防疫層面都剩係向權貴同共狗負責<br />\n<br />\n免檢疫令影響共狗佢邊膽搞，平民防疫就多多限制<br />\n<br />\n就正如當日黑警射清真寺就仆到去道歉，平民被搞就理撚得你"},{"pid":"8f744ac3c9d427515851caa798ec27d9d9f44b41","tid":2114983,"uid":35418,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:41:21.000Z","msg":"林奠: 初選令疫情急速惡化<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce3dec469018cc9d8682d48fba62f6b4e51bd859","tid":2114983,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:44:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd99ed759738504c3e29a2ae3ff1dec44fc22b5","tid":2114983,"uid":89517,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T09:00:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"835d844c3f520c7117181b85dcac49ec3582de3e","tid":2114983,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12faec01bd024f9356bb296c1b4fb320ad4a6685","tid":2114983,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"呢單我有印象，係9個貨船水手去到寧波確診，中途站係香港，唔係9個寧波人係香港確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國籍就標準水手果種mix乜春窮國都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de07cf86c35a3bf69b83a6c465a3ee0960a1fe1d","tid":2114983,"uid":19055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T10:43:41.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">政府放毒，市民防疫<br />\n不如真攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"5d11c8b0d07c1ab1e2ebe0516aa801cf67f2a804","tid":2114983,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"835d844c3f520c7117181b85dcac49ec3582de3e","tid":2114983,"uid":38255,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"12faec01bd024f9356bb296c1b4fb320ad4a6685","tid":2114983,"uid":264426,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:21:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T10:41:43.000Z","msg":"呢單我有印象，係9個貨船水手去到寧波確診，中途站係香港，唔係9個寧波人係香港確診<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n國籍就標準水手果種mix乜春窮國都有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-20T10:47:44.000Z","msg":"搵到果陣既報導<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n衞生防護中心接獲<del>內地</del>支那海關通報一宗涉及11人的確診個案群組。他們均為貨櫃船MSC Flavia的船員，該船原定於6月26日於寧波登岸，全船共有24人，當中11名船員抵達寧波時，被當地海關驗出對病毒病呈陽性反應。<br />\n<br />\n當中9名外籍船員曾先後於6月21日至23日期間抵港，他們屬於豁免強制檢疫人士，獲公司安排入住荃灣帝盛酒店。值得留意的是，該酒店地址鄰近葵涌嘉里物流貨倉，即早前有4名員工確診的小型爆發地點。<br />\n<br />\n11名船員中，9人於6月24日在香港登上貨櫃船，當中6人由印尼、2人由希臘及1人由克羅地亞於6月21日至23日期間抵港。"}],"pinned":{"pid":"d0d14f22c7a9608e50084612ccbf3f120bba0dc3","tid":2114983,"uid":123774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-19T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"林鄭4點記招完全冇講收緊免檢疫令<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}}